[
    {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "INTAMBARA IKOMEYE",
        "description": "Iyi ni ngeri ya kabiri y’igitabo “Intambara Ikomeye Hagati ya Kristo na Satani”. Muri iyi ngeri, ibidatunganye byagaragaye mu ya mbere byarakosowe, kandi igitabo cyateguwe hakurikijwe umwimerere w’icyongereza “The Great Controversy Between Christ and Satan”.\r\n\r\nIki gitabo gisobanura intambara iri hagati y’icyiza n’ikibi kuva mu mateka ya kera, gusenyuka kwa Yerusalemu, kugeza ku bihe bya nyuma no kugaruka kwa Kristo. Gitera kwizera, kigakomeza umutima w’abizera kandi kikabategurira ibihe bya nyuma.",
        "file_path": "content/documents/6a3ec62e8d038.pdf",
        "cover_image": "content/documents/covers/6a3ec630668a8.jpg",
        "download_count": 1,
        "is_published": 1,
        "deleted_at": null,
        "created_at": "2026-02-28 22:28:59",
