    },
    {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "IBYAKOZWE N’INTUMWA",
        "description": "Ibyakozwe n’Intumwa” ni igitabo cya kane mu ruhererekane rw’ibitabo bisobanura amateka yera. Gisobanura inkuru itangaje y’itorero rya mbere nyuma y’uko Yesu amaze gutsinda Satani agasubira mu ijuru.\r\n\r\nIki gitabo kigaragaza uburyo umwanzi yahanganye n’itorero rya Kristo ku isi, binyuze mu gutotezwa gukomeye no kugerageza kwizera kw’abakristo ba mbere. Petero, Pawulo, Yakobo, Yohana, Luka, Barinaba, Sitefano, Mariko n’izindi ntumwa zatwaye ubutumwa bwiza ku isi yose yari izwi icyo gihe.\r\n\r\nNubwo benshi batanze ubuzima bwabo kubera kwizera kwabo, ubutumwa bwiza bwakomeje gukwira hose. Inkuru iracyakomeza no muri iki gihe, kuko itorero rya Kristo rikomeje umurimo umwe kandi rifite amasezerano amwe yo kuyoborwa n’imbaraga z’Imana.",
        "file_path": "content/documents/6a3ec6366419d.pdf",
        "cover_image": "content/documents/covers/6a3ec6381e554.jpg",
        "download_count": 0,
        "is_published": 1,
