    {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "UWIFUZWA IBIHE BYOSE",
        "description": "Uwifuzwa Ibihe Byose” ni ubutumwa bushingiye ku kuri ko mu mitima y’abantu bose, hatitawe ku bwoko cyangwa urwego rw’imibereho, habamo icyifuzo gikomeye cyo kubona icyo badafite.\r\n\r\nIki cyifuzo cyashyizwe mu muntu n’Imana y’inyambabazi, kugira ngo atanyurwa n’ubuzima bwe bwa none cyangwa ngo yishimire ibyo agezeho gusa. Imana yifuza ko umuntu ashakisha icy’ingenzi kirenze ibindi byose — ukuri, agakiza n’ubugingo buhoraho.\r\n\r\nUbu butumwa burahamagarira buri wese gushaka iby’iteka, no kwakira umugisha w’ubugingo bw’ibihe bidashira.",
        "file_path": "content/documents/6a3ec63faa470.pdf",
        "cover_image": "content/documents/covers/6a3ec6417f888.jpg",
