    {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "Prophets and Kings",
        "description": "Prophets and Kings” is the second volume in the five-book series explaining sacred history. Though written later, it presents a powerful overview of the lives of Israel’s prophets and kings.\r\n\r\nThrough decades of ministry, Ellen G. White revealed that behind human history stand unseen forces — the hand of God working in righteousness and the opposing power of the enemy. This book connects biblical history with the ongoing spiritual conflict between good and evil.",
        "file_path": "content/documents/6a3ec6487967b.pdf",
