    {
        "id": 7,
        "title": "Patriarchs and Prophets",
        "description": "Patriarchs and Prophets is the first volume in the sacred history series. It covers biblical history from the creation of the world to the reign of King David.\r\n\r\nWhile presenting ancient events, the book reveals deeper spiritual meanings, explaining the motives behind human actions and highlighting the great conflict between good and evil.\r\n\r\nIt demonstrates that biblical history is not merely narrative but a powerful source of instruction capable of transforming lives and producing lasting change.",
        "file_path": "content/documents/6a3ec697723ed.pdf",
