        "id": 8,
        "title": "Counsels on Diet and Foods",
        "description": "Counsels on Diet and Foods” presents practical guidance on nutrition and its impact on physical, mental, and spiritual health.\r\n\r\nEllen G. White emphasized the importance of wholesome diet and balanced living long before modern scientific research confirmed its value. This book provides timeless principles for healthy Christian living.",
