    {
        "id": 9,
        "title": "Testimonies for the Church – Volume 1",
        "description": "Testimonies for the Church – Volume 1  contains spiritual counsel given to guide God’s church in preparation for the return of Christ.\r\n\r\nSeventh-day Adventists eagerly await the second coming of Jesus, when sin, suffering, sickness, and death will be no more.\r\n\r\nThis volume is drawn from Ellen G. White’s earliest published works, including Christian Experience and Views (1851), Supplement to Christian Experience and Views (1854), and Spiritual Gifts, Volume 1 (1858).\r\n\r\nIt provides foundational instruction for Christian character development and spiritual readiness.",
